subsequently we get to it. See, I was in the 
Southeast Asian War, like you were, and I was

23:55.645 --> 24:00.231
assigned Thailand. I was Deputy Commander of 
1312th Air Force. It, uh... Udorn, and I visited

24:05.797 --> 24:11.907
the detachment up at Chiang Mai, Thailand, the 
very air base that I hit, if I'm not kidding. That

24:11.947 --> 24:14.431
must have been fascinating.

24:25.368 --> 24:29.955
So it's north of Bangkok. Chiang Mai is the Summer 
capital, here we are, Chiang Mai. It's Chiang Mai.

24:38.334 --> 24:39.795
So it's close to the Burma border. Yeah, it's right 
across the Burma border.

24:44.781 --> 24:45.882
It's the Saline River. Northwest Thailand. 
Northwest Thailand, yeah. C-H-A-N-G-M-A-I.

