25:17.724 --> 25:28.457
were taking Burma, so why come up at Lower Wing and 
suffer air defense missions and lose airplanes

25:17.724 --> 25:28.457
like they've been losing at Rangoon? So... We 
weren't engaging them. The old man began to get

25:32.307 --> 25:35.672
impatient, so we began to figure out how to... So 
